snippet.textDisplay: Sadly, for this particular classical part we have so many talented enriched classical singers in our country.. you hear a spell from a pure classical ostad and bam ! you just know this is magic ! May be they don’t have connection like her with you guys. She is good here like any other good singer…on tune correctly…but she doesn’t add anything special in this part. This is international level platform- you have resources-we would love to see our classical ostads to represent us to world…..I mean you did good work on folk genre previously…I wish we could show our classical gems too. And you know how this would have boosted up the song in just another level if we could bring our classical legends .
snippet.textOriginal: Sadly, for this particular classical part we have so many talented enriched classical singers in our country.. you hear a spell from a pure classical ostad and bam ! you just know this is magic ! This is international level platform- you have resources-we would love to see our classical ostads to represent us to world…..I mean you did good work on folk genre previously…I wish we could show our classical gems too. snippet.textDisplay: I loved the way Sunidhi is interacting with all her co-artists. What a respect! Very few of them have shown this on this stage. It's a rare thing to witness! Sometimes I came back only to watch this, honestly. IT WAS a team effort and she acknowledged it. This is what a heart of an artist should be like, broad and pure mashallah. This is one of the greatest fusions in Bangla music industry, I would say. And the twist that begins and carries on from 5:50-Ammmmmmmmaaaaazing!!🙂
